description:
This is a 15 minute workout called '15 Min Intense HIIT Workout For Fat Burn & Cardio (No Equipment, No Repeats)' from the channel Oliver Sjostrom.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Firestarter vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: 15 min Full Body HIIT with a variety of high intensity strength and cardio movements, great for both burning fat and building strength.
